[Student "S"]
{EAST wants to be in game but doesn't know which one. 
If WEST holds three \Hs she would prefer 4\H, 
otherwise she would try 3NT. EAST bids 2\S, Fourth Suit Forcing.

WEST denies three \Hs but confirms a \S honor by 
bidding 2NT, so EAST bids the game in Notrump.}

